113
00:08:08.479 --> 00:08:10.479
"Sawako Kouzuki (35)"

114
00:08:10.479 --> 00:08:12.879
Terima kasih banyak.

115
00:08:12.879 --> 00:08:14.479
Siapa dia?

116
00:08:14.479 --> 00:08:16.779
Dia anak tunggal Tuan Kouzuki, Sawako.

117
00:08:17.979 --> 00:08:20.679
Mungkin peta ini tidak ada hubungannya dengan pencurian,

118
00:08:20.679 --> 00:08:23.879
